CHAIR:
I move to amend amendment HB3287 FULLPCS1
Of the printed Bill
Page 2 Section 1 Lines 17-19
Of the Engrossed Bill
By deleting all language beginning with the word "promulgate" on Line 17
through the word "signage" on Line 19 and inserting in lieu thereof, the
following language: "make the signage available for print on the public
website of the Department. Hospitals and health care facilities may
request that the signage be mailed to the hospital or health care facility
for the cost of printing and first class postage".
AMEND TITLE TO CONFORM TO AMENDMENTS
